# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your actual values.

## Clerk Authentication
# Get these from https://dashboard.clerk.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Clerk redirects (usually don't need to change these)
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/sign-in
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/sign-up
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/dashboard
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/dashboard

## Supabase Database
# Get these from https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-supabase-service-role-key

## Anthropic AI
# Get your API key from https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

## Optional: App URL (for production deployments)
# Set this to your production domain
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://yourdomain.com
